enb_long_title: Eleventh session of the Conference of the Parties to the Climate Change Convention and first meeting of the Parties to the Kyoto Protocol
sentences: SBSTA agreed to the report of the session (FCCC/2005/SBSTA/L.15).
Chair Benrageb thanked delegates for their hard work.
Many Parties thanked Chair Benrageb for his excellent efforts over the past two years, and the Chair declared SBSTA 23 closed shortly after 1:30 am.
